item.description: Would you like to know the cause of your medical symptoms? Maybe you'd like to know what vitamins or minerals you are lacking, or what foods you should eat or avoid... Join Vera Sacks, Certified Electrodermal Stress Analysis Technician as she shows you how to get the answers you've been looking for in this FREE introduction and demo. Experience the use of EDS in helping to identifying imbalances within the body and in offering suggestions to help restore the body to a more balanced (and thus healthier) state. Find out first hand what EDS is all about!
